{"tid":1803964,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"樂曈向新戲監製李璨琛𢱑撈 33歲女甘願做奶媽","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:05:57.000Z","uid":186431,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1cba34fca56bcdc14c067d3d8b4211837e1462","tid":1803964,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdENKH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdENKH4.jpg&h=eef71890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節對唔少藝人嚟講係搵錢機會，對樂瞳嚟講更係𢱑撈好時機。入行12年歌又唱過，劇同戲都拍過，但無咩歌曲或者角色令人特別難忘，不過佢一直無放棄演藝事業，新一年希望樂瞳有更多機會啦。<br />\n<br />\n李璨琛成立新公司囡囡Lucy成最細新人幫手宣傳<br />\n<br />\n李璨琛趁聖誕節帶同囡囡Lucy(元元)，以及由佢監製嘅新戲《大盜演》一眾演員包括樂瞳、姜文杰、潘伯仲、鄺家瑜(MaryJane)等齊齊報佳音，而小Lucy更以可愛聖誕造型亮相撐爸爸，李璨琛笑言：「成立公司後會簽新人，好開心簽咗年紀最細嘅新人Lucy，佢知爸爸有新戲，仲自薦做宣傳！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10RgC3k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10RgC3k.jpg&h=22014744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4eYRon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4eYRon.jpg&h=2c65e6fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂曈向李璨琛𢱑撈 33歲女甘願做奶媽<br />\n<br />\n化身性感聖誕女郎嘅樂瞳邊逗小Lucy玩，邊向李璨琛𢱑撈：「好多謝監製畀呢個機會我，下次可唔可以再搵我？」李璨琛回應：「好啦！下次你就嚟做奶媽⋯⋯哈哈！應該話做保母。」樂瞳食住上：「奶媽我都ok，照顧晒大家！」咁抵得諗，相信李璨琛下次都會預埋佢嘅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bs3F4JT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbs3F4JT.jpg&h=99b18ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於新戲中飾演李璨琛分居老婆嘅樂瞳，為求𢱑撈不惜自薦做奶媽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teCcbo4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteCcbo4.jpg&h=6c25b34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想屌奶媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8999a49eae017ec903f81650cea29cdf16cd3805","tid":1803964,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"冇奶"},{"pid":"35d17f6663d7bc51928b25274e0da01234ce4b5b","tid":1803964,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=c5794caa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9e8f1ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要33000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=ebff88c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國聯署 deadline 3/1<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-geno